GSD.description:
net/mlx5e: Avoid false lock dependency warning on tc_ht even more

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.1.9 by commit d8da8d96ff1de02266daa24c94bf02610da88cf6, it was introduced in version v5.12 by commit 9ba33339c043addc4aee241fd7ac37593f7c9e7e. For more details please see the references link.
